Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:31.01,Titel,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,590)\fs70\c&H1010A4&}Faceless One
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:59.78,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}The blue moon illuminated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:03.75,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}your wandering shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:08.25,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}I could never tell you all I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:13.17,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,250)}It was so very frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:17.05,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}I think about your faked smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:21.68,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}and forget all the hot tears we shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:24.35,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}What do these empty husks,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.39,0:01:30.19,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}those empty eyes of yours, reflect, my dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:35.40,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}The transient quarter moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:37.57,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,100)}hides in a rift in the clouds,
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.53,0:01:39.95,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(100,300)}as darkness seeps up from the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:44.41,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}Tell me the truth, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:46.58,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}Are you so despondent
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:50.96,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,0)}that you still sit alone, sighing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:54.42,Titel,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(990,615)\c&H1010A4&}Part the Second
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:09.95,Titel,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(990,615)\c&H1010A4&}The End
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feelings and memories…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.56,0:00:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They exist only within my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though we may pass the same time, or see the same sights,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what we hold within our hearts can never be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face, your voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the image of you, which exists only within me…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m afraid I won’t bend to your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you will not show me your true Form, then at least
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,be quiet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a contrary thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, shall we restart our little play?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Play?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The intertwined fates of men give the Mononoke its Form.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:03:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When an Ayakashi clings onto\Na person’s thoughts and feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it becomes a Mononoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:07.66,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You came here to kill the Mononoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:09.79,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(640,617,640,690,200,0)\t(50,200,\c&HE9ECF1&\3c&H262B32&)}I see. You came here to kill the Mononoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could kill it now, my work would be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must discover the Mononoke’s Truth and Regret,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and without its Form,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot draw the Sword of Exorcism.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a troublesome Mononoke, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth is a physical state,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Regret is a state of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Mononoke will not show me its Form,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will have to make it tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,its Truth and Regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochou’s life,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Part the First.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My{\alpha&HFF&} life?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My life?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sake! Sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need more sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to bring me more sake! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a worthless wife you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mononoke is showing me what you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The perfect feelings for a Mononoke to leech.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a laughing matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes it is. Quite funny, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With such a laughable situation as an excuse,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how many{\alpha&HFF&} did you kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how many did you kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the result of relying on the Mononoke’s strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relying on…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you{\alpha&HFF&} remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your very own sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which you watched every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My own{\alpha&HFF&} sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My own sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to bring me more sake! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I—I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You simply looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was only looking, but it made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you not leave this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it that you really killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:25.90,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did I really kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.03,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:33.16,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(640,616,640,690,200,0)\t(50,200,\c&HE9ECF1&\3c&H262B32&)}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochou-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who did you{\alpha&HFF&} kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who did you kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Step no further into Ochou-san’s heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochou-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you believe this place binds you, it will be your prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do not wish to leave, it will become a fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the same as that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought of it as a prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to bring me more sake! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:22.88,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I—I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:23.46,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(640,619,640,690,200,0)\t(50,200,\c&HE9ECF1&\3c&H262B32&)}I—I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I not simply leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:08:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look just like I did when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With your beauty, you will certainly\Nbe able to marry into a wealthy family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is most difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Ochou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t have to tell him anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is deceiving you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The play is not over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochou’s life,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Part the Second.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were born beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.13,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your appearance carefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:52.88,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:09:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you will be able to marry into a wealthy\Nfamily, in spite of your humble upbringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good girl. Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted her praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you bore it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the point of losing your own soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My{\alpha&HFF&} soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times must I say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve warned you about that so many times!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.51,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I’m sorry!{\alpha&HFF&} I’m sorry! I’m sorry! I’m sorry! I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:38.64,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I’m sorry! I’m sorry!{\alpha&HFF&} I’m sorry! I’m sorry! I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:39.93,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I’m sorry! I’m sorry! I’m sorry!{\alpha&HFF&} I’m sorry! I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:41.39,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I’m sorry! I’m sorry! I’m sorry! I’m sorry!{\alpha&HFF&} I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:42.77,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I’m sorry! I’m sorry! I’m sorry! I’m sorry! I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start over from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:44.48,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I’m sorry!{\alpha&HFF&} I’m sorry! I’m sorry! I’m sorry! I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:46.14,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I’m sorry! I’m sorry!{\alpha&HFF&} I’m sorry! I’m sorry! I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:47.77,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I’m sorry! I’m sorry! I’m sorry!{\alpha&HFF&} I’m sorry! I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:49.52,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I’m sorry! I’m sorry! I’m sorry! I’m sorry!{\alpha&HFF&} I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:51.02,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I’m sorry! I’m sorry! I’m sorry! I’m sorry! I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll never be a proper lady at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:10.79,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}One and two and three!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:14.80,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Four and five and six!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:18.88,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Seven and eight and nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hid myself, so as not to interrupt your taking of vows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochou’s life,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Part the Third.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I merely wish to express my\Ngratitude and extend my best wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, sit up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We derive no pleasure from watching you prostrate yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My goodness, such a gorgeous lady she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you as good in bed as you look?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s for our brother to find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can buy as many women as I want with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, keep her for all her life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:05.10,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your mother’s wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:06.14,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:07.93,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,My father died young, and his pension was confiscated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:09.39,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(640,616,640,690,200,0)\t(50,200,\c&HE9ECF1&\3c&H262B32&)}My father died young, and his pension was confiscated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All my mother wished was for me to marry into wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the only thing she wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can finally hold my head high as I visit\Nthe graves of my ancestors, the Umezawake clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you became your mother’s tool, to further her ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:33.83,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost your soul for your mother’s wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:12:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You became a tool for your mother’s selfish ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you fell in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the object of your affections…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochou’s life,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Part the Fourth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to bring me more sake! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I—I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochou-san, just get us some more sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a worthless wife you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lazy girl, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, whyever did you take her in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her mother begged me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your first wife hadn’t hung herself, would\Nyou ever have accepted her into your home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she’s a pretty good cook,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and good in bed, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh stop, you’re just terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochou-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who did you kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it. Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:13:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochou-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that mask is not
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a Mononoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Mononoke{\alpha&HFF&} controls the masked man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Mononoke controls the masked man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It deceived you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and imprisoned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is its Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in trying to accept{\alpha&HFF&} your mother’s twisted love,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in trying to accept your mother’s twisted love,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:35.02,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,No!{\alpha&HFF&} No! No! No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:37.06,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!{\alpha&HFF&} No! No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your heart wavered, and a Mononoke latched onto it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.19,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! No!{\alpha&HFF&} No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:39.60,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! No! No!{\alpha&HFF&} No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:40.65,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! No! No! No!{\alpha&HFF&} No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the Regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.94,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! No! No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can fulfill my dream and marry into wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:06.05,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I did my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did my best, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, listen! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:23.15,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}Mother, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:26.48,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won’t you listen to what I have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:29.07,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(640,616,640,690,200,0)\t(50,200,\c&HE9ECF1&\3c&H262B32&)}Why won’t you listen to what I have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All four of these men are wealthy and prosperous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:36.41,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, why won’t you listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:39.33,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(640,617,640,690,200,0)\t(50,200,\c&HE9ECF1&\3c&H262B32&)}Mother, why won’t you listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}I can’t wait. I can’t wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.59,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t wait. I can’t wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:49.05,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}I can’t wait. I can’t wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:52.51,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t wait. I can’t wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:55.68,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it{\alpha&HFF&} that you killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it that you killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did I
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost yourself in others’ greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:47.19,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a Mononoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your Form.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Mononoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I{\alpha&HFF&} ask you one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask you one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did the Faceless One…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you believe you were saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish to know,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,perhaps it fell in love
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His love could never be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mononoke{\alpha&HFF&} despaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mononoke despaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mononoke{\alpha&HFF&} despaired?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mononoke despaired?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to bring me more sake! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I—I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochou-san, just get us some more sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a worthless wife you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lazy girl, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, whyever did you take her in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her mother begged me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your first wife hadn’t hung herself, would\Nyou ever have accepted her into your home?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she’s a pretty good cook,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and good in bed, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh stop, you’re just terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lazy bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re totally useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s so damned lazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:16.11,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Useless indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can’t you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She lazes around so, whatever she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can’t stand her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s taking her so long, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sake! Sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring us sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where’s the sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there’s{\alpha&HFF&} no-one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there’s no-one{\alpha&HFF&} here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there’s no-one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:19.25,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}Without you, I just can’t smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:30.31,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}I walk this banal town,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:36.39,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}feeling such intense emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:42.78,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}I know that if I could treasure them and live on,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:52.08,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}I would need nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.74,0:22:00.25,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}The summer flowers that bloomed in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.25,0:22:06.55,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}Come falling down, dancing in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.63,0:22:09.89,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}I can barely recall the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:13.18,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}where they all came tumbling down,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.18,0:22:24.03,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}so what I can still recall is all the more precious.
